name: Prepare Traveller 3D Techdemo
description:
Hello Busy people

This is Uncharted like Game Prototype

this is one of my old game concepts "Prepare Traveller" Which was made in unity 

The Games ideas and vision are same but with high-quality 3d graphics and new places to explore 

There is gameplay in it but I classify this as just "a tech demo with some relevant gameplay"

__________"MadeinUnreal5"___________________

This is my first UE5 Andriod app! , High-performance mobiles variants can play this tech demo

Desktop Verison is also available -> can be played with Controller using DS4 or Mouse and keyboard

The desktop version is superior to mobile version 

Controls

Screen Joystick, touch screen to jump
